title: My acoustic version of Kayle & Morgana theme :3

body:
I had a lot of fun recording this, and absolutely love this music theme that Ed the Conqueror from Riot composed >< like usual

This piece is very hard to sing and both chords and time signatures are very unconventional, so forgive me if I don't sound as good as you expect. 

Thanks so much 

{{sticker:sg-ahri-2}}
